name: Special Delivery (itch) (Juan_O)
description:
A fast food delivery guy must make his last delivery of the day, in a former residence in the most remote area of the city.
  • ASWD o Arrows - Move
  • Z - (A) Interact.
  • X - (B) Notes.
  • Enter - Pause.
  • Shift (Select) - Items.

Alternative Endings.

Made using  GB STUDIO by Chris Maltby.

Art by JuanO.
